                    "text": "30,000 gp",
                    "value": 30000,
                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "Some luck blades contain one wish when crafted. You can cast this spell as an arcane innate spell while wielding the luck blade , expending the spell. A spellcaster who can cast wish can place another wish into the blade by spending 8,000 gp and 4 days of downtime. A wishing luck blade can hold no more than one wish at a time.",
